		""
		"&71.&r Pipe 200+ mB heavy oil into the tower (same controller as crude)"
		"&72.&r Collect &ftfmg:lubrication_oil&r — the distinctive second-pass product"
		"&73.&r Bonus outputs: more diesel, kerosene, naphtha"
		""
		"&cCommon mistakes:&r"
		"&7• Only coking heavy oil — distillation recovers liquids before coke"
		""
		"&7JEI:&r &ftfmg:distillation/heavy_oil&7"
