		"&7Routes:&r 4× sand crafting, Create gravel compaction + water, or bulk sand belts from crushing."
		""
		"Stock &f8× sandstone&r before heated lithification quests."
		""
		"&7JEI:&r &fminecraft:sandstone&7 · &fkubejs:building_stones/calcite_lithification&7"
